09:38.101 --> 09:57.325
partly grown up in China, and going to my 
grandfather's house and seeing all these

09:57.963 --> 10:06.073
wonderful Chinese chinoiserie and stuff like 
that that he brought back with him. I have always

10:06.173 --> 10:14.282
been interested in China, studied Chinese when I 
was in college, studied it some more when I got

10:06.173 --> 10:14.282
here. And so that was yet another connection with 
Joan and Harlem, which I always was very fond of.

